Span.Text: Enable first responders to populate mapping software with critical information to track development, identify areas needing support, and monitor their assets in the area.  Microsoft technologies and partner solutions address many of these capabilities, including: Real-time crime centre, Incident management, Situation awareness, Computer-aided dispatch (CAD) and Neighbourhood management.  Gather and analyse large volumes of structured and unstructured data (e.g., text, photos, video, social movement) to gain insights and viewpoints that help improve response coordination and effectiveness.
